com.aliyun.oss.common.utils

类 CRC64

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aliyun.oss.common.utils.CRC64
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Checksum

    public class CRC64
extends Object
implements Checksum
    CRC-64 implementation with ability to combine checksums calculated over different blocks of data. Standard ECMA-182, http://www.ecma-international.org/publications/standards/Ecma-182.htm
